<span id="freeTextContainer1467258356164327272">This is an engrossing, well-paced biography that is a pleasure to read. I&apos;m left with a deep and motivating admiration of many facets of Leonardo&apos;s character, especially his eager mind, attention to detail, thinking from first principles, his use extensive use of physical notebooks, and, most intriguingly, his use of art as a thinking tool. It&apos;s fascinating to get a glimpse of someone so far ahead of his time, and it&apos;s fun to think about what he would make of today.</span>
  <span id="freeText1467258356164327272" style="display:none">This is an engrossing, well-paced biography that is a pleasure to read. I'm left with a deep and motivating admiration of many facets of Leonardo's character, especially his eager mind, attention to detail, thinking from first principles, his use extensive use of physical notebooks, and, most intriguingly, his use of art as a thinking tool. It's fascinating to get a glimpse of someone so far ahead of his time, and it's fun to think about what he would make of today.</span>
